title: Button for deletion of rune pages faster not working
body: I don't know if other people have the same problem, is not much of a big deal but is kind of annoying... I can't turn that button to delete rune pages faster. Any solution. Thanks :)

replies.body: I've been waiting for someone else to post on this it's been like 3 weeks for me!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!
I have the same issue, can delete pages in them but that button does not work.
